room_title: Escape room "The Mad Hatter" by Escape Strategy in Chicago
room_description: Alice has fallen down the rabbit hole and ended up at the craziest of tea parties. You have met her there and with the “help” of the Hatter need to get Alice back to the real world before the queen of hearts takes all your heads. You must answer the Hatters questions and work your way back through the illusions of Wonderland.
